<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>FAQs | Cosmetic Store</title>
<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    background:#f5f5f5;
}
.container{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:60px auto;
    background:#fff;
    padding:50px;
    border-radius:16px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
h1{
    color:#c2185b;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}
.faq-item{
    margin-bottom:25px;
}
.faq-item h3{
    margin:0 0 8px;
    color:#333;
}
.faq-item p{
    margin:0;
    color:#666;
    line-height:1.6;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Are your products 100% original?</h3>
        <p>Yes. All products are authentic and sourced directly from verified brands.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How can I track my order?</h3>
        <p>You can track your order from the <b>My Orders</b> section after login.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What payment methods are available?</h3>
        <p>We accept UPI, Debit/Credit Cards and Cash on Delivery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I cancel my order?</h3>
        <p>Yes, orders can be cancelled before dispatch from My Orders.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
